Dame mi dinero, imbécil.

00:33:23.280 --> 00:33:25.920
Oye, pequeña...

00:33:25.920 --> 00:33:26.960
¡Oye!

00:33:30.050 --> 00:33:31.960
Cielos, no.

00:33:37.260 --> 00:33:38.560
-Cielos.
-Cielos.

